* {{ill|Okagami Shrine (Kawasaki City)|ja|岡上神社 (川崎市)}} (おかがみじんじゃ) - A Shinto shrine located at 809 Okagami, {{ill|Asao Ward|ja|麻生区}}, {{ill|Kawasaki City|ja|川崎市}}, {{ill|Kanagawa Prefecture|ja|神奈川県}}.<ref>[https://www.kanagawa-jinja.or.jp/search_dtl.php4?jid=95&cd=1201095&scd=&npg=0 Okagami Shrine (おかがみじんじゃ)] Kanagawa Prefecture Shrine Association</ref><ref name="Asao Tourism"/>  
