* {{ill|Okanoue Shrine (Itano)|ja|岡上神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okanoue Shrine (Itano)|qq=}} (おかのうえじんじゃ) - A [[:en:Shinto shrine|Shinto shrine]] located in [[:en:Itano, Tokushima|Itano Town]], [[:en:Itano District, Tokushima|Itano District]], [[:en:Tokushima Prefecture|Tokushima Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Okagami Shrine (Kawasaki City)|ja|岡上神社 (川崎市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okagami Shrine (Kawasaki City)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (おかがみじんじゃ) - A Shinto shrine located at 809 Okagami, [[:en:Asao-ku, Kawasaki|Asao Ward]], [[:en:Kawasaki, Kanagawa|Kawasaki City]], [[:en:Kanagawa Prefecture|Kanagawa Prefecture]].<ref>[https://www.kanagawa-jinja.or.jp/search_dtl.php4?jid=95&cd=1201095&scd=&npg=0 Okagami Shrine (おかがみじんじゃ)] Kanagawa Prefecture Shrine Association</ref><ref name="Asao Tourism"/> ** {{ill|Kami|lt=Kami|lt=Deities|ja|祭神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Deities|qq=}}: {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ヤマトタケル}}, {{ill|Takeminakata-no-Kami|ja|建御名方命|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeminakata-no-Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to タケミナカタ}}, [[:en:Oyamakui no Kami|Ōyamakui-no-Kami]], {{ill|Ukanomitama-no-Mikoto|ja|倉稲魂命|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ukanomitama-no-Mikoto|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ウカノミタマ}}.<ref name="Asao Tourism"/> ** In 1909 (Meiji 42), five local shrines in {{ill|Okagami Village|ja|岡上村|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okagami Village|qq=}} were merged under the name "Okagami Shrine." The site of the former {{ill|Suwa Shrine|ja|諏訪神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suwa Shrine|qq=}} in the center of the village was chosen for the new shrine to promote unity among villagers.<ref name="Asao Tourism">[https://asao-kankou.jp/?page_id=1992 Okagami Shrine (おかがみじんじゃ)] Asao Tourism, Kawasaki/Asao Tourism Association, accessed January 6, 2022.</ref> See also {{ill|Okagami#Facilities|ja|岡上#施設|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okagami#Facilities|qq=}} and {{ill|History of Okagami Village|ja|岡上村#歴史|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/History of Okagami Village|qq=}}. * Okagami Shrine (おかがみじんじゃ) - The former name of {{ill|Okanomiya Shrine (Fukaya City)|ja|岡廼宮神社 (深谷市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okanomiya Shrine (Fukaya City)|qq=}}, located in [[:en:Fukaya, Saitama|Fukaya City]], [[:en:Saitama Prefecture|Saitama Prefecture]].
